{"tid":757674,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"認真，就嚟行街都要考牌","createTime":"2018-07-27T05:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T11:57:56.000Z","uid":165355,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"719e79bd0aff10f6ff635ba816075880931d7fb9","tid":757674,"uid":165355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T05:00:34.000Z","msg":"日日喺街都俾人一字型排開慢行塞住成條路<br />\n我唔係好趕時間，亦唔係行得好快<br />\n但係唔想跟住你哋啲龜速步伐噉虛耗光陰<br />\n<br />\n發覺男女老幼都有呢個問題<br />\n廢老嘅話我唔理啦，頂多畀佢玩多幾年都落地獄<br />\n啲C9/啊叔係噉，後生一代又係噉<br />\n特別係班00後，好似成條街都係屬於佢哋噉<br />\n街、電梯，甚至搭車... 自己有位就乜撚都唔理<br />\n<br />\n同佢哋講句唔好意思/唔該借借又西口西面<br />\n唔講仲以為係我阻撚住條街<br />\n好心唔好咁撚自私啦 理得你幾大班人都好<br />\n盡量靠一邊行或者留條通道畀人過係常識嚟啫 <br />\n行街都要人教<br />\n條路闊嘅話，你點樣亂行都唔理你啦<br />\n<br />\n00後要教，連老豆老母都要教"},{"pid":"03f6ae6b6646810ffddba9e30793dec57a578359","tid":757674,"uid":9115,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T05:04:09.000Z","msg":"特別係d女人行行下突然停低揄襪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c42562ccc205fdbd3594bbbd127b3957102bc4","tid":757674,"uid":39576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T05:06:51.000Z","msg":"除咗一字排開仲有望左右甚至後面但向前行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb99093a0602b209788a8931a2b0cc6316c651a7","tid":757674,"uid":163791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T05:09:56.000Z","msg":"行行下 停低 屌你老母玩微信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f76bffb8b1a2f4b14b7b1690fb574ddabb6c8c2a","tid":757674,"uid":165355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03f6ae6b6646810ffddba9e30793dec57a578359","tid":757674,"uid":9115,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T05:04:09.000Z","msg":"特別係d女人行行下突然停低揄襪<img src=\"/asse